2.1.1
-----

 * Add --savebatch=filename
   Saves the current URL batch to a file (for later use).
   Useful when dealing with multiple batches as ~/.config/clive/recall
   batch gets overwritten over time. the specified file is not overwritten,
   instead a numeric suffix is appended to the filename.

